{You need to find out about Aces so you bid 4NT. Partner says 6\D.  

Partner has shown one Ace and a \D void. As to what you bid, that's easy. You have no choice now but to say 6\H. This is a pretty good slam, but it is not cold. Maybe West will not lead a \C. Or maybe East will have the \DA.}

